## About mountainbikeorientering.se

**Mountainbikeorientering.se** is the premier hub for MTBO in Sweden. We gather news, schedules, and information to grow the sport and support both elite and recreational cyclists. Whether you are a beginner looking for your first race or a seasoned pro, this is your community. This subsite is the dedicated home for the 2026 World Championships, created to serve the international community.
